{"tid":1790654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍屍拎刀追斬手足，警方回應：沒有需要自首","createTime":"2019-12-20T07:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T18:53:05.000Z","uid":222970,"like":28,"dislike":278,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f877b11b832ef3d5db84873c00eb664e2591be","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"地盤工9.1持刀作勢追斬示威者 今認罪辯稱警指暫不需自首<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMY9jHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMY9jHY.jpg&h=0e08a7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告當日持刀(紅圈)作勢追斬示威者。<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n網民早前發起「901機場見」活動，圖堵塞交通並妨礙機場運作，及後爆發警民衝突，大批示威者徒步離開機場前往東涌。當日下午，有地盤工在東涌逸東邨附近持刀作勢追斬示威者及街坊，市民爭相走避，有市民拍下事發片段。地盤工今在西九龍裁判法院承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，求情稱持刀只是為嚇人，更謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事後已問警方需否自首，警方卻回應暫沒有需要。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n被告蔡彼得（45歲）早前否認控罪，案件原定今預審，惟被告改口認罪。裁判官劉綺雲押後案件至明年1月8日，待索閱被告的背景報告及翻看涉案片段後始判刑，其間被告須還柙。劉官明言，會考慮判處被告坐監。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱涉案刀具未開鋒<br />\n<br />\n早前未有律師代表的被告，今透過當值律師求情指，對事件感到後悔，明白所作所為並不恰當，勇於接受法律懲罰。被告亦明白社會近期的糾紛不易解決，希望各方平和理性地處理，盡快回復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續稱，被告沒政治取態，沒預謀犯案，亦非聯同他人行事。辯方又透露，被告事後曾主動致電警方，詢問需否自首，惟警方回應暫不需要；及至9月23日，被告住所遭人塗鴉，心理造成極大負擔，亦感連累家人，兩日後被捕。至於涉案刀具，辯方透露<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">刀鋒長15厘米，只是裝飾品</span></span>，未有開鋒，被告只旨在嚇唬他人，又指他追趕市民一段距離後便停下，未有揮動。劉官要求控方在押後判刑期間，查證辯方所言是否屬實。<br />\n<br />\n警誡下承認犯案 辯稱自衛<br />\n<br />\n案情指，警方於9月1日驅散在機場進行的示威行動，示威者打算離開大嶼山。及後網上流傳片段，可見身穿白衣的被告在東涌逸東邨巴士總站附近持刀，接近約30名示威者。警方其後找到拍攝片段的女子，她稱當日傍晚6時許聽到有人在街上大叫，及後看見被告持刀追向示威者，於是用手機拍下過程，並傳給親友。<br />\n警方其後上門拘捕被告，被告警誡下承認犯案。被告在警誡錄影會面中稱，當日與他人在青衣爭執，並遭跟蹤至東涌，於是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回家拿刀放進背囊內以作自衞</span></span>。他及後在巴士總站看見早前與他爭執的男子，男子向他丟膠樽等雜物，他遂持刀追趕他們。被告稱案發後已將刀丟掉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHttAjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHttAjV.png&h=1ee8d575&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"308c4c89783b7bb96a7f44b5206a4d37ac79e97a","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":65,"dislike":18,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y39o8BX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy39o8BX.jpg&h=ec1b1669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abedfd6c3dfd74a4232c3f58c6fe827ace9c7c11","tid":1790654,"uid":9256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308c4c89783b7bb96a7f44b5206a4d37ac79e97a","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":65,"dislike":18,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y39o8BX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy39o8BX.jpg&h=ec1b1669&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a9cb133a7dbf0f7a62ed8a3c5042a176bbc67502","tid":1790654,"uid":37722,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0490f24ae4a937db777e732ccdeb02d5e1585fd","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>爛尻法院同黑警合作破壞香港，屌你老母臭閪玩撚曬<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n#屯門裁判法院第一庭 - 張潔宜署理主任裁判官<br />\n#手足報料<br />\n劉(25)🛑已還押88天 📢#判刑 管有攻擊性武器 #0921元朗 早前認罪，解釋指當日只是「捱義氣」幫其他人帶走武器，武器上並沒有他的指紋<br />\n判監‼️12個月‼️"},{"pid":"36e6f489871af2a858635e39f5029add5b216b35","tid":1790654,"uid":51057,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】月餅餐刀當攻擊武器 警拘浸大學生記者19小時才釋放<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0916 23:26 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0916 01:05<br />\n<br />\n【新增警方回應】<br />\n昨晚（15日）11時許，警方在炮台山道清場期間，6名身穿標示「記者」和「Press」反光衣和頭盔的學生記者上前採訪，但遭警方截停，要求出示記者證和身份證，再搜查其隨身物品。其中浸大學生記者蘇敬華因袋中留有一把用來切月餅的餐刀，被指持有攻擊性武器，遭警方帶上私家車。記者多次追問防暴警，會送被捕記者到哪間警署，警員均未有回應。蘇敬華在北角警署被扣留約19小時才獲釋。<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】反修例催生HKDC連繫港美 首要任務爭取通過《人權法案》<br />\n<br />\n昨晚被截查的其中4人，均為浸大「廣播新聞網」記者。受查的譚同學指，警方當時沒有表明搜查原因。被捕的學生蘇敬華，是浸大「廣播新聞網」學生記者。據了解，他亦是now兼職員工。蘇同學在警方搜查期間，在袋中搜出一把餐刀。同行同學解釋，該同學前日外出時因切月餅攜帶餐刀，昨日忘記取出。惟女警不相信，反指「好難不懷疑」。<br />\n港島總區高級警司（行動）吳樂俊今午出席警方記者會，死撐在場警員專業，聲言同事「必定有原因」說服自己「合理」拘捕對方，若警方最終沒有足夠證據，就不會檢控。有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級警司李桂華反指，該名被捕學生當時並非採訪，只是與一些示威人士於現場徘徊，警員覺得他可疑，於是上前截查，結果搜出一把「9吋長金屬尖刀」。雖然被捕學生解釋，該把刀是早前中秋賞月時用來切月餅，但警方不接納。李聲稱警方拘捕對方，與其行業及年紀無關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我屌你老母呀死警甴</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f4e9471062f839764ddf960608bf96f36c2c8831","tid":1790654,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"佢又肯認罪"},{"pid":"850d9d64425eecada494293292f8bae07e8a0975","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f4e9471062f839764ddf960608bf96f36c2c8831","tid":1790654,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"佢又肯認罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"班黑警教佢 肯認罪 黑警死攬佢"},{"pid":"dadce8330807f2eae67ed3867b2346cfcd6a64a0","tid":1790654,"uid":42981,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"算唔算教唆證人/疑犯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7343073cce69e6f12780f9643ed60384a76d51e8","tid":1790654,"uid":200786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f4e9471062f839764ddf960608bf96f36c2c8831","tid":1790654,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"佢又肯認罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"應該好難打得甩所以先叫佢認罪"},{"pid":"2df751f650c2c3a44985912bd8cd8ab5350dcf04","tid":1790654,"uid":119232,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"學生文宣就話非法用途<br />\n藍絲拎刀就話裝飾品<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d3d7825c509b64de34980a8c2222c98f4d3422","tid":1790654,"uid":271857,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"傳統華人都喜愛黑社會。<br />\n以大欺小，恃強凌弱，<br />\n以武力威嚇多於以公義服人。<br />\n華人歷史就係黑社會歷史<br />\n由一幫黑社會消烕另一幫黑社會<br />\n打贏黑社會大佬就叫皇帝<br />\n而家大陸也是行這一套。<br />\n幸台灣改改為民主制度，<br />\n但仍有不乏少數傳統長者喜愛黑社會文化。"},{"pid":"59434dd633a6c7ef8a8c346884686b9138f41ee5","tid":1790654,"uid":269481,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"把刀未開鋒都up得出，喺屋企拎把未開鋒嘅刀出黎做咩呀？把刀都俾你掉撚左你話乜都得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943a20620b6134960cd1dc9a29af3919ef0bdbeb","tid":1790654,"uid":45120,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"肯燒法院未<br />\n毫無法治可言<br />\n你試吓喺運動之前咁講野<br />\n話咩裝飾 自衛？<br />\n睇吓個官屌唔屌撚死你？<br />\n<br />\n雷射筆又話傷人<br />\n行山杖雨遮又話傷人<br />\n我屌你老母 你唔跟規則玩點解我地仲妄想用制度去制裁呢班人"},{"pid":"d5c70189df44e88fb78db0023d3f58d88cea27db","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7343073cce69e6f12780f9643ed60384a76d51e8","tid":1790654,"uid":200786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f4e9471062f839764ddf960608bf96f36c2c8831","tid":1790654,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"佢又肯認罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"應該好難打得甩所以先叫佢認罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"告得入  但一定社會服務令同感化令 <br />\n頂多緩刑 肯撚定唔使坐監！！！"},{"pid":"0bda1b40ec791a58180a9cc42d56926056e1b8f8","tid":1790654,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5c70189df44e88fb78db0023d3f58d88cea27db","tid":1790654,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7343073cce69e6f12780f9643ed60384a76d51e8","tid":1790654,"uid":2007